==English==
===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} [[chimera]]. The [[fabulous]] monster in [[Lycea]] 
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Chimaera'''

#{{greekmyth}}: Fantastical [[monster]] in [[Lycea]] with the head of a [[lion]], [[goat]] and [[serpent]] which vomited fire. Killed by the hero [[Bellerophon]].

